{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"15":"Jihad (Kitab Al-Jihad)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2557,"arabicnumber":2557,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا مُسَدَّدٌ، حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الْوَارِثِ، عَنْ أَيُّوبَ، عَنْ نَافِعٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ، قَالَ نُهِيَ عَنْ رُكُوبِ الْجَلاَّلَةِ","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":15,"hadith":81}}]}